&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/LAS-VEGAS-MARQUEE-DAY-OFFER-LOGO1.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-8339&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/LAS-VEGAS-MARQUEE-DAY-OFFER-LOGO1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;LAS VEGAS- MARQUEE DAY- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;274&quot; height=&quot;40&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;Marquee Dayclub at The Cosmopolitan of Las Vegas spans 22,000 square-feet of the expansive multi-level Marquee Nightclub &amp;amp; Dayclub entertainment complex and boasts two pools, several bars and a gaming area. Programming throughout the season is highlighted by Marquee Nightclub &amp;amp; Dayclub resident DJs encompassing the world&rsquo;s premier electronic music talent. Exclusive experiences can be had in one of the grand cabanas, which feature infinity edge glass dipping pools, flat screen televisions and dedicated cocktail and food service. The ultimate day to night offering will be discovered in the exclusive bungalows dotting the perimeter of the Dayclub, complete with overnight quarters, individual pools and an open-air party deck. Days spent dancing or basking in the sun is made complete with well thought out amenities while a specialty cocktail and food menu from Corporate Executive Chef Ralph Scamardella fuels the party.&nbsp;Swimwear casual attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please send an email to&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:lifestylelv@taogroup.com&quot;&gt;lifestylelv@taogroup.com&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;to make your reservation.&nbsp;Provide&nbsp;your name, date you would like to attend, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address. You will be provided with all details and instructions for general admission or table/bottle service reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ages 21 &amp;amp; Over. ID must be provided.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Benefit is applicable for up to 2 guests in total.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dress code will be strictly enforced. Management reserves the right to refuse entry to guests due to visible intoxication, lack of proper ID, failure to adhere to dress code, or capacity limits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access is granted only with reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Late arrivals past midnight will be required to pay any required cover charges, despite having a reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Nightlife&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Diners Club Card must be used for payment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Nightlife Access benefit may not be combined with other offers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Nightclub/Lounge merchant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reservations&nbsp;based on availability at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nightclub/lounge participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blackout dates may apply due to event buyouts. Special event/DJs may incur a charge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

